OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry but cloudy morning with
OL,6,Flow cloud and some misty patches
OL,7,Fpossible, brighter spells possible in
OL,8,Fthe west. Cloud breaking up from late
OL,9,Fmorning to give some long sunny spells
OL,10,Fin the afternoon. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with late
OL,13,Fsunshine, then long clear spells after
OL,14,Fsunset. Overnight will be dry with
OL,15,Flong clear spells, but a few mist and
OL,16,Ffog patches possibly forming.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
